Subject: [security bulletin] HPSBHF03310 rev.2 - HP Thin Clients running Windows Embedded Standard 7 (WES7) or Windows Embedded Standard 2009 (WES09) with HP Easy Deploy, Remote Elevation of Privilege, Execution of Code

